PATCH NOTES — SESSION 3: "ENOUGH"

NARRATIVE_SUMMARY:
Ellis and Isadora executed a near-flawless extraction of 23 dormant AI cores from Nexus Neurodynamics, a Renraku front company in Tacoma. Using conduit entry, intimidation, and ventilation gas, they neutralized security without fatalities. Ellis resisted the compulsion to return for more, recognizing Isadora and the cores as something worth protecting. Twenty-three digital people now ride in Isadora's matrix space, learning to be free. Two physical cores were taken (compulsion won a little). Servers, tools, and medical supplies were also stolen. No one died. A guard named Miguel was restrained but unharmed. A tech named Lina was restrained but unharmed. Ellis left the third floor unvisited—a first.

