-------RESUME GAME HERE-------

Redmond Garage. 5:47 AM. The van hums quietly. Twenty-three new passengers sleep in digital space, exhausted by freedom. Isadora is quiet—not absent, just... resting. Processing.

Miller waits at 4th and Lander. 6 AM. Thirteen minutes.

The servers sit in the van, full of stolen data. Two physical cores pulse softly. 980k¥ incoming in ~36 hours.

And somewhere in the dark, the Unknown Third Party is learning that their account was emptied, their contract tampered with, their prey still breathing.

What do you do, Ellis?
